OL,6,FMore than 30,000 people were infected
OL,7,Fwith deadly viruses while they were
OL,8,Freceiving NHS care between the 1970s
OL,9,Fand 1990s,
OL,11,FSir Brian said "the scale of what
OL,12,Fhappened is horrifying", with more
OL,13,Fthan 3,000 people dead as a result and
OL,14,Fsurvivors battling for decades to
OL,15,Funcover the truth.
OL,17,FIt has been labelled the "worst
OL,18,Ftreatment disaster in the history of
OL,19,Fthe NHS."
